            {
              "id": "booking_calendar_embed",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "html",
              "settings": {
                "html": "<!-- Overture / Calendly booking calendar embed -->\n<!-- Replace the src URL below with your Overture or Calendly embed URL -->\n<!-- Overture embed: Overture Admin \u2192 Booking Pages \u2192 Embed Code -->\n<!-- Calendly embed: calendly.com/[your-username]/discovery-call -->\n<div style=\"min-width:320px; height:700px;\">\n  <iframe\n    src=\"https://calendly.com/xcphotographyuk/discovery-call\"\n    width=\"100%\"\n    height=\"700\"\n    title=\"Book a Discovery Call with XC Photography\"\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    sandbox=\"allow-forms allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"\n    allow=\"payment; geolocation\"\n    style=\"border: none; border-radius: 4px;\"\n  ></iframe>\n</div>",
                "_element_custom_width": "100"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "booking_info_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 40,
            "_column_size_tablet": 100,
            "_column_size_mobile": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "booking_what_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "What Happens on the Call?",
                "header_size": "h3",
                "typography_font_family": "Raleway",
                "typography_font_size": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "size": 22
                },
                "typography_font_weight": "700"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "booking_what_text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<ul style='list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 30px;'><li style='padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>\ud83c\udfaf &nbsp;<strong>We learn about your brand</strong>: your goals, your audience, and the story you want to tell.</li><li style='padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>\ud83d\udcf8 &nbsp;<strong>We explore your vision</strong>: the look, feel, and emotional impact you're aiming for.</li><li style='padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>\ud83d\udca1 &nbsp;<strong>We share ideas</strong>: concepts, locations, and approaches that fit your brand perfectly.</li><li style='padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>\u2705 &nbsp;<strong>We assess fit</strong>, because the best work happens when photographer and client are genuinely aligned.</li><li style='padding: 10px 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;'>\ud83d\udccb &nbsp;<strong>Next steps</strong>: if it's a great fit, we'll outline a tailored proposal. No pressure either way.</li></ul>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "booking_duration_box",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<div style='background: #1a1a1a; color: #ffffff; padding: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #E8E4DC; margin-bottom: 30px;'><p style='margin: 0 0 6px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #E8E4DC;'>The Details</p><p style='margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7;'>\ud83d\udcc5 <strong>30 minutes</strong> via Zoom or phone<br>\ud83d\udccd Available UK-wide<br>\ud83c\udf81 <strong>Completely free</strong>, no obligation<br>\u23f1 Response within 24 hours of booking</p></div>"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "booking_prefer_form",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p style='font-size: 15px; color: #555; line-height: 1.7;'>Prefer to reach out by email first? <a href='/contact' style='color: #1a1a1a; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline;'>Use the contact form \u2192</a></p>"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "booking_faq",
      "elType": "section",
      "settings": {
        "_title": "Booking FAQ",
        "layout": "boxed",
        "content_width": {
          "unit": "px",
          "size": 900
        },
        "background_background": "classic",
        "background_color": "#ffffff",
        "padding": {
          "unit": "px",
          "top": "80",
          "right": "20",
          "bottom": "80",
          "left": "20",
          "isLinked": false
        }
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "faq_col",
          "elType": "column",
          "settings": {
            "_column_size": 100
          },
          "elements": [
            {
              "id": "faq_heading",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
                "header_size": "h2",
                "align": "center",
                "typography_font_family": "Raleway",
                "typography_font_size": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "size": 36
                },
                "typography_font_weight": "700"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "faq_accordion",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "accordion",
              "settings": {
                "tabs": [
                  {
                    "tab_title": "Do I need to prepare anything before the call?",
                    "tab_content": "Not at all. Just show up as you are. If you have a few thoughts about your brand or some visual references you love, feel free to share them, but it's absolutely not required. The conversation will naturally surface everything we need."
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "How quickly will I get a proposal after the call?",
                    "tab_content": "If we're a great fit, you'll receive a tailored proposal within 48 hours of your discovery call. It will include a recommended package, an outline of what we'll create together, and investment details."
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "What if I'm not ready to book but want to learn more?",
                    "tab_content": "That's completely fine. The discovery call is exactly the right place to start. There's no expectation to commit on the day. Many of our best client relationships began with a relaxed exploratory conversation months before the shoot."
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "Do you work with clients outside Brighton?",
                    "tab_content": "Yes, XC Photography shoots across the UK. We travel for the right brief. Travel costs for locations more than 50 miles from Brighton are outlined transparently in your proposal."
                  },
                  {
                    "tab_title": "What if I need to reschedule?",
                    "tab_content": "No problem at all. Use the reschedule link in your booking confirmation email, or email hello@xcphotography.uk and we'll sort it within the hour."
                  }
                ],
                "active_item": 1,
                "title_html_tag": "h4",
                "title_typography_font_family": "Raleway",
                "title_typography_font_weight": "600",
                "title_typography_font_size": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "size": 17
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
